@NODE magazine "Message to Magazine Reviewers !!"
If you are a magazine reviewer I strongly recommend that you drop me an
@{"email" link contact}. There are many reasons for doing this.
I like to read reviews about my applications, but I cannot read every Amiga
magazine in the world. Sending me email guarantees that I will buy a copy of
your magazine !!
Misunderstandings can easily be sorted out, and I need your opinion in
order to improve this application.
@ENDNODE
@NODE history "MrSPLIT's history"
                                  History
                                  -------
v1.1    Added a cut with offset function as requested by Peter (luke).

        Found and removed a Wipeout hit. I used memory after it was freed.

        Didn't cleared the outputFilename-buffer, so the filename could be
        corrupt on some systems.

        Called an OS function even when it wasn't needed.


v1.0	First public release.
@ENDNODE
